subject: Used 12-470 on ebay, but is it old version?
author: M.A. Coletta (Mike)
full_text:
Good Morning All,
There is a used 12-470 on ebay right now.  The description says used 12-
470, but the picture appears to be of the old 12-469 (no speaker and 
additional letters at bottom. Older 12-470 only says, "DIGITAL STEREO" 
at bottom, the one pictured says more).
You might want to contact the seller to ask what the case actually 
looks like before you bid.
It's on ebay here:
http://cgi.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ViewItem&item=320204138852&ru

- Mike
